title: HELMS DEEP UNDER SIEGE - Third Age Total War Gameplay [Historical Battle]
description:
Third Age Total War Gameplay - A new power is rising!  10,000 Uruk - Hai march to the gates of Helms Deep.  Theoden and his men are out numbered, but there is always hope!  Enjoy the Siege! 

This is an updated custom scenario of Helms Deep, made by Paladinbob.
